Datanglah makan malam apabila awak lapang.

00:32:02.510 --> 00:32:04.370
Baoying asyik bercakap tentang awak.

00:32:05.070 --> 00:32:06.530
Dia dah bertambah tinggi, kan?

00:32:08.160 --> 00:32:10.490
Pegawai bandar telah datang melawat anda.

00:32:10.590 --> 00:32:11.920
Semoga awak cepat sembuh.

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:13.750
Baiklah.

00:32:13.790 --> 00:32:14.310
Ayuh.

00:32:14.510 --> 00:32:15.370
Pengarah Chen,

00:32:15.400 --> 00:32:15.930
dengan cara ini.

